                "invention-title": [
                    "Light energy utilization device for coupling concentrating photolysis water hydrogen production with photovoltaic and photo-thermal power generation",
                    "一种聚光光解水制氢耦合光伏光热发电的光能利用装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a light energy utilization device for coupling light-concentrating water splitting hydrogen production with photovoltaic and photo-thermal power generation, which comprises a light-concentrating power generation system, a solar cell panel and a water splitting hydrogen production system, and is characterized in that the light-concentrating power generation system comprises a light concentrator and a light splitting device; the light splitting device is installed in the condenser and used for dispersing light with the wavelength larger than the preset wavelength and light with the wavelength smaller than the preset wavelength. The solar cell panel is installed at the tail end of the condenser and used for receiving light with the wavelength larger than the preset wavelength, one end of the solar cell panel is connected with a thermoelectric assembly, and the thermoelectric assembly is electrically connected with an electric energy storage device. The solar energy utilization device has the beneficial effects that the technical problems that in the prior art, a light energy utilization device cannot comprehensively utilize heat energy and light energy in sunlight, the danger of explosion caused by mixing of hydrogen and oxygen in the using process is avoided, and the safety performance of the light energy utilization device in the using process is improved are solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种聚光光解水制氢耦合光伏光热发电的光能利用装置，包括聚光发电系统、太阳能电池板和光解水制氢系统，所述聚光发电系统包括聚光器和分光装置；所述聚光器内部安装有所述分光装置，所述分光装置用于将波长大于预设波长的光线与波长小于预设波长的光线分散；所述太阳能电池板安装于所述聚光器末端并用于接收波长大于预设波长的光线，所述太阳能电池板的一端连接有热电组件，所述热电组件与电能储存装置电连接。本发明达到的有益效果是：解决现有技术中光能利用装置，无法全面利用太阳光中的热能和光能，且在使用过程中不会出现氢气和氧气混合引发爆炸的危险，提高光能利用设备使用过程中安全性能的技术问题。"
                }
            ]
